Success
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The target gains the Obsessed Condition (Persistent), with regards to their
 guilt.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Depending on their current Integrity this manifests in varying ways (and
 as they decline, the symptoms change):
\end_layout

